Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BandMatrix
    BandMatrix is a special type of matrix that contains a band down the top-left to bottom-right diagonal.
    BlockMatrix
    The block matrix is a special kind of matrix where there are square blocks aligned on the diagonal from the top left to the bottom right.
    Entry
    An entry in a sparse matrix.
    SquareSparseMatrix
    A class for storing and operating on sparse two dimensional matrices.
    SquareSparseMatrixTester
    A class to test SSM and the 3 special matrix classes.
    TriangleMatrix
    The TriangleMatrix is a special kind of matrix where there are numbers in a triangular format on the bottom left or top right of the grid.
